%t A363346 A363346list[nmax_]:=Module[{ca=CellularAutomaton[86,{{1},0},{2nmax,{-nmax+1,nmax}}]},Array[Length[First[FindTransientRepeat[Drop[Diagonal[ca,nmax-#],Ceiling[(#-1)/2]],2]]]&,nmax]];A363346list[100]
